{"id":579373,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/02/【立此存照】修宪登基话题-网络言论控制措施一览/","date":"2018-02-26T04:24:34Z","modified":"2018-02-26T07:49:07Z","title":"【立此存照】修宪登基话题 网络言论控制措施一览","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>中国官方宣布将取消习近平任期限制后，墙内各社交网站除迅速开始大面积删除网民议论外，还采取了更多辅助手段进行言论控制，如社交平台禁止修改用户名、头像等个人信息；甚至有网游也无法修改用户名；百度搜索不提供“移民“等关键词数据；微博搜索结果白名单化，只显示蓝V账号内容等。</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：中国数字空间｜</strong><strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%8D%81%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%A8%E4%BC%9A\">十九届三中全会</a></strong></p></blockquote>\n<h4>1. 从2018年2月25起至3月底，微博、微信、QQ、知乎等不能改用户名、昵称、头像、签名等信息</h4>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3957.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579380\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3957.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3957.jpg 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3957-300x154.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微信改名.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579388\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微信改名.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"690\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微信改名.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微信改名-174x300.jpg 174w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微信改名-768x1325.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/微信改名-594x1024.jpg 594w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3955.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579382\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3955.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3955.jpg 487w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3955-300x203.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<h4>2. 甚至有网游也不能改用户名</h4>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3914.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579384\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3914.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"498\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3914.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3914-241x300.jpg 241w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3841.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579385\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3841.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3841.jpg 1102w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3841-300x182.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3841-768x466.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3841-1024x621.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3841-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<h4>3. 百度搜索“移民“搜索量暴涨被疯传后，已不提供“移民“等关键词数据</h4>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_579386\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3840.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-579386\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3840.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3840.jpg 1260w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3840-300x202.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3840-768x518.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3840-1024x691.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_579379\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/百度移民.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-579379\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/百度移民.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"96\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/百度移民.jpg 1444w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/百度移民-300x52.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/百度移民-768x134.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/百度移民-1024x179.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">百度指数搜索结果截图</span></p></div>\n<h4>4. 微博搜索结果白名单化，只显示蓝V账号内容</h4>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3907.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579396\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3907.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"350\" height=\"622\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3907.jpg 1242w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3907-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3907-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3907-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3906.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579397\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3906.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"350\" height=\"598\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3906.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3906-176x300.jpg 176w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3906-600x1024.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/fil