tps://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3910.jpg 1242w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3910-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3910-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3910-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3909.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579394\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3909.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"350\" height=\"622\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3909.jpg 1242w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3909-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3909-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/IMG_3909-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>5.部分商业类微博公号（如被网友过度解读+恶搞的 @迪士尼中国 @杜蕾斯官方微博）已基于审查压力关闭了最新用户评论。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/迪士尼中国的微博.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-579413 aligncenter\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/迪士尼中国的微博.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"406\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/迪士尼中国的微博.png 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/迪士尼中国的微博-300x271.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/迪士尼中国的微博-768x694.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/杜蕾斯官方微博的微博.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-579414\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/杜蕾斯官方微博的微博.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"328\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/杜蕾斯官方微博的微博.png 903w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/杜蕾斯官方微博的微博-300x219.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltime